MELT,Metadata,Ecology,for,Learning,and,Teaching,is,a,project,designed,to,provide,people,who,use,educational,content,with,access,to,more,useful,types,of,metadata,The,goal,is,to,help,them,to,find,resources,that,fit,their,needs,in,terms,of,language,culture,and,preferred,teaching,style,MELT,is,provided,by,the,German,FWU,Institut,fuer,Film,und,Bild,FWU,has,contributed,about,learning,objects,and,assets,to,the,MELT,repository,These,resources,can,be,accessed,through,the,MELT,website,or,by,using,the,SOAP,based,API,The,MELT,website,is,provided,in,both,English,and,German